wikilambda-emptylabel: Default label shown for a ZObject that doesn't have one yet.
wikilambda-invalidzobject: Error shown when an invalid ZObject definition edit is made.
wikilambda-invalidcontenttype: Error shown when a non-ZObject is attempted to be saved on a ZObject page.
wikilambda-labelclash:
Error shown when a ZObject is attempted to be saved with a clashing label.

Parameters:
* $1 - The ZID of the clashing page.
* $2 - The language in which the other page's label clashes.
wikilambda-multilingualstring-nofallback: Message shown when a multi-lingual string doesn't have a label defined for the user's language, nor for any of that language's fallbacks.
wikilambda-speciallistduplicatezobjectla: Message shown on Special:ListDuplicateZObjectLabels when there are not duplicates.
Column header on Special:ListDuplicateZObjectLabels, showing a link to the original ZObject with the label.
Column header on Special:ListDuplicateZObjectLabels, showing a link to the newly-conflicting ZObject with the label.

Column header on Special:ListDuplicatZObjectLabels, showing the language in  which the two ZObjects have a conflicting label.
